   The VR Edition of the critically acclaimed BAFTA award-winning Hellblade:
   Senua's Sacrifice.

   From the makers of Heavenly Sword, Enslaved: Odyssey to the West, and DmC:
   Devil May Cry, comes a warrior's brutal journey into myth and madness.

   Set in the Viking age, a broken Celtic warrior embarks on a haunting
   vision quest into Viking Hell to fight for the soul of her dead lover. 

   Created in collaboration with neuroscientists and people who experience
   psychosis, Hellblade: Senua's Sacrifice will pull you deep into Senua's
   mind.

   Note that Hellblade does not support motion controls.

